OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1783779570
OL,3,CAmber heat health alert extended to
OL,4,CWednesday for South West
OL,6,FThe amber heat health alert for the
OL,7,FSouth West has been extended.
OL,9,FThe warning issued by the UK Health
OL,10,FSecurity Agency (UKHSA) for the region
OL,11,Fwas due to end on Sunday evening, but
OL,12,Fis now in place until 9pm on Wednesday
OL,13,F15 July.
OL,15,FThis means significant impacts are
OL,16,Flikely across health and social care
OL,17,Fservices due to the high temperatures,
OL,18,Fincluding a rise in deaths,
OL,19,Fparticularly among those aged 65 and
OL,20,Fover, or with health conditions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
